![From the scatterplot matrix we can see that the outliers are present in PC5, PC6 and PC7. That means by reducing the dimensionality to the first four PCs the model has missed some important characteristics in the data.](pca_files/figure-html/fig-plane-o-n-pairs-1.png){#fig-plane-o-n-pairs width=672}
:::
